OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly start with some early
OL,6,Ffrost in places with bright or sunny
OL,7,Fspells through the day. The risk of a
OL,8,Ffew showers around, these mainly in
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. Feeling slightly warmer
OL,10,Fthan Wednesday.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FAny remaining shower ease
OL,13,Fovernight but returning from the south
OL,14,Fby dawn. Clear spells in the east but
OL,15,Fmost areas staying frost free.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FA mostly dry start to the day
OL,18,Fwith the odd light shower. These
OL,19,Fturning heavier into the afternoon
OL,20,Fwith some daytime heating. Feeling
OL,21,Fwarmer than recent days in any sun.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
