OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,6,Fmixed weekend with showers in places,
OL,7,Fbut bright or sunny spells not far
OL,8,Faway. Staying mostly dry into the new
OL,9,Fweek but temperatures will start to
OL,10,Fdrop.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
